text:
*Attention 1st Years- Cougar Capital Info Session 10/10*

Come join us on Tuesday evening to hear more about one of the MBA’s LDBs, Cougar Capital! Cougar Capital is an investment fund modeled after VC/PE firms where students get the chance to research, present, and ultimately invest in companies alongside some of the top investment firms in the state/nation. There will be multiple members of the current Cougar Capital class there to share their experiences and backgrounds. We will also go over important dates/requirements to get into Cougar Capital. See below for a little more information:

When: This Tuesday (10/10) from 5-6 PM
Where: W208

Any and everyone is welcome! Please come with questions, and we will try to answer all of them!
